{"tid":2128700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"689參選大會司儀潘麗瓊化名Now傳媒人「施嘉雯」出書後稱 ： 名字沒有專利","createTime":"2020-07-28T06:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:20:26.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e561c401a643d4f0520dce2ee68a771cdc029eb8","tid":2128700,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:29:51.000Z","msg":"今日（28 日），曾任前特首梁振英參選造勢大會司儀的專欄作家潘麗瓊，終披露上述文章由她執筆，筆名亦由她所擬。潘麗瓊指「名字不是任何人的專利」，如果有誤會就澄清，批評外界對此事語帶嘲諷和抹黑，甚至牽連同書其他作者。潘又稱，自己不想用筆名只是因應負責編輯的要求。然而根據施嘉雯引述該著作負責編輯、《亞洲周刊》副總編輯江迅的說法，作者是因為「不願用自己的真名」才採用筆名。<br />\n<br />\n潘麗瓊今日在《頭條日報》專欄表示，「我向以真名示人，對文章負責」，是因為該書主編江迅要求，「他希望每位作者只貢獻一篇文章，結果我交了兩篇共兩萬字的長文」。潘麗瓊在書籍出版前都希望繼續用真名，但主編說為免破壞規矩，要求她其中一篇用筆名，結果「我隨意用夫家『施』姓，再用我英文名 Carmen 音譯『嘉雯』刊出，就希望盡量用真名出現。」就此，潘在文章向施嘉雯致歉，又指自己和她不熟，「落此筆名時，沒想過是要人誤會是她。當施小姐向我查詢此事時，我請她向主編查詢，就是基於我和主編的君子協定。」<br />\n<br />\n潘最後表示，「<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">名字不是任何人的專利。如果有人誤會了，澄清就是了</span></span></strong>，為何要牽連其他作者如屈穎妍、雷鼎鳴、馬恩國及馮煒光呢？還要語帶嘲諷，以抹黑為目的。我不敢苟同。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%88%86%E5%92%AA%E5%A7%90-%E6%BD%98%E9%BA%97%E7%93%8A%E5%8C%96%E5%90%8D-%E6%96%BD%E5%98%89%E9%9B%AF-%E6%92%B0%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E6%B2%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E5%90%8C%E5%90%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%A7%93%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A-%E5%85%B6%E5%BF%83%E5%8F%AF%E8%AA%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E6%25BD%2598%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2593%258A%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%2590%258D-%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%259B%25AF-%25E6%2592%25B0%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25A7%2593%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%25A8%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25AA%2585%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=a78857e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E6%25BD%2598%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2593%258A%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%2590%258D-%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%259B%25AF-%25E6%2592%25B0%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A7%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25A7%2593%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%25A8%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25AA%2585%2F&h=2b1452cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%88%86%E5%92%AA%E5%A7%90-%E6%BD%98%E9%BA%97%E7%93%8A%E5%8C%96%E5%90%8D-%E6%96%BD%E5%98%89%E9%9B%AF-%E6%92%B0%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E6%B2%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E5%90%8C%E5%90%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%A7%93%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A-%E5%85%B6%E5%BF%83%E5%8F%AF%E8%AA%85/</a>"},{"pid":"6c0148cf1e247da3a508cba3253d580147ff5672","tid":2128700,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"懶人包：<br />\n<br />\n藍絲作者唔敢用真名 竟然用左Now工作既施嘉雯做筆名 出版界表示同情不過無能為力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2126730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2126730</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1835e01584cdc31c7e461e38070ffd1a3841e927","tid":2128700,"uid":37680,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"佢都知自己個朵臭過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d021cfaf56dc85de4c74fd9833f8e8ef0a03794","tid":2128700,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:32:28.000Z","msg":"真係痴線<br />\n用人地啲人氣"},{"pid":"598ba23d0f0d7c0b937c6f0331f7b0db6e85c079","tid":2128700,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:33:20.000Z","msg":"柒到仆街<br />\n<br />\n你方個施嘉雯知道唔會出黎澄清？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本冇人理而家個個知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083bff215a820df9121d560ba1d05228f8b65b23","tid":2128700,"uid":55011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"咁你唔改做習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2234fabb2f4c7c0784f7460a4056395ec448c2c","tid":2128700,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"咁你唔用習近平? 鄭月娥?"},{"pid":"d4cf599e7a308db14cf891f2bd9d19db7897040c","tid":2128700,"uid":54516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"呢條女之前頭條出過專欄老作天使。<br />\n既然名冇專利，我用佢個名借錢或者寫甜故得唔得皮?"},{"pid":"944b1355de86bbd3246e7c4b249c0cb62302ef9b","tid":2128700,"uid":21505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"咁我係咪可以用習近平做筆名？"},{"pid":"0d2e1ed1677f01145e61c14678655419a48368f5","tid":2128700,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"即係以後可以代言雜種 林鄭 CY"},{"pid":"dbc69c074522c44d55c127aa16e9730741530a6a","tid":2128700,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"鬼鬼祟祟"},{"pid":"7a347d65421446e803cd301bcc0bb3d066524519","tid":2128700,"uid":37111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"其他共狗屈穎妍、雷鼎鳴、馬恩國及馮煒光都用真名喎<br />\n得你係咁 狗都不如"},{"pid":"f90168fd9f766cc0c4d24360a7809cc316131d15","tid":2128700,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a347d65421446e803cd301bcc0bb3d066524519","tid":2128700,"uid":37111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"其他共狗屈穎妍、雷鼎鳴、馬恩國及馮煒光都用真名喎<br />\n得你係咁 狗都不如"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"共蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8610469bc58a4a8647c9430a11863cc9cb86aad7","tid":2128700,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"如果之後d專欄寫手抱不平用晒佢個名出文就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b868563494d483230c9270920e7498437e1c63","tid":2128700,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"用習近平做筆名出第一身gay故書有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a735296ecae102d8a377ee981cdd5110a7ab6774","tid":2128700,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"好撚核突 地球癌細胞"},{"pid":"a0c7653ecd9b926de91f5cc552ac475f703fe1f3","tid":2128700,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"人閪有樣睇 成件死人妖咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMqoefz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMqoefz.jpg&h=1c94e36f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b8fd255979fe55333036e6fd4fcb51f5546febd","tid":2128700,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出書"},{"pid":"671d6c3d88d91897eba478e149080968dc7a1589","tid":2128700,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"//最近，大家聞「武漢色變」，親友知我二月到武漢公幹，以為我去送死！<br />\n<br />\n  雖然目前泰國有一個女遊客發現有武漢肺炎，但香港根本連「一」個武漢不明肺炎個案也沒有。就連懷疑個案也是「零」！醫管局天天公佈的武漢肺炎疑似個案不斷上升，但仔細看，絕大部份都是已知病因的流感，例如甲型H3流感、甲型H1流感（未公佈病因只是未有檢驗結果）。<span class=\"red\"><strong>患者接受沙士冠狀病毒測試，結果都是陰性的，卻大部份公眾「冇看」清楚武漢肺炎，以為「武漢肺炎香港大爆發」，自己嚇自己。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n  武漢肺炎所以惹起沙士疑雲，是因為擔心它是新變種的沙士冠狀病毒，會人傳人。但世衞前天發表聲明，指出中國由新型冠狀病毒引發的肺炎，「疫情尚未擴散到武漢以外地方，亦未有證據顯示會人傳人。」亦未有醫護人員受感染。<br />\n<br />\n  由去年十二月二十九日至今天，已超過十四天，以醫學常識判斷，迄今沒有大爆發，此肺炎的擴散力有限。我們要審慎留神，但不需要大恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n <span class=\"red\"><strong> 正如傳媒人黃永稱，真正傳染力度高的，不是武漢不明肺炎，而是「鹵莽不明廢言」！</strong></span>容易受感染的是不看客觀事實的「驚咗先」群眾，立法會內有議員，為了討好民眾，要求政府向武漢發出外遊警示<span class=\"red\"><strong>。即使世衞已經出聲明了，但香港官員也不能斬釘截鐵地說：「武漢肺炎並未擴散至香港，亦非人傳人」</strong></span>，反而是天天宣佈疑似個案正在增加，造成不必要的恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>  真正無可救藥及不斷傳染的，不是武漢肺炎，而是「冇看肺炎」，不看客觀事實，政治盡情操弄、新聞熱烈炒作，社會被無知和恐懼侵蝕。由人性衍生的病毒，最難消滅。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">潘麗瓊</span></strong></span>//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁點解潘文妓你呢篇警世鴻文又唔用藝名出嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5532a93e4502ff34cbb774ed16e08705f96256f","tid":2128700,"uid":278697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"潘麗瓊話「黑警洗全加」<br />\n<br />\n利申，係阿邊個邊個嘅筆名"},{"pid":"d8ce47ccc2f55ce1a536b5abe6ee2c26b2493ab6","tid":2128700,"uid":278697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0c7653ecd9b926de91f5cc552ac475f703fe1f3","tid":2128700,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"人閪有樣睇 成件死人妖咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMqoefz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMqoefz.jpg&h=1c94e36f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"打厚格啊！<br />\n唔該！"}]}